{"word":"περιδίδωμι","slug":"περιδίδωμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n81257\" key=\"peridi/dwmi\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">περιδίδωμι</orth>, only in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <sense id=\"n81257.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stake, wager</tr_>, c. gen. pretii, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρίποδος περιδώμεθον ἠὲ λέβητος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">let us make a wager of</tr_> a tripod, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">let us wager</tr_> a tripod (to be paid by the loser), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:485\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.485</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐμέθεν περιδώσομαι αὐτῆς</foreign> I <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">will wager</tr_> myself, i.e. my life, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:23:78\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.78</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. πότερον</foreign>. . <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lay a wager</tr_> whether . . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1115\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ach.\">Ach.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1115</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">περὶ τῆς κεφαλῆς περιδόσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:791\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">791</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : with dat. pers. added, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περίδου μοι περὶ θυματιδᾶν ἁλῶν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have a wager</tr_> with me for a little thyme-salt, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:772\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ach.\">Ach.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">772</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περίδου νυν ἐμοί, εἰ μὴ</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:644\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">644</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0447.tlg001:130\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Diph.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">130</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}